links.title: Qualcomm enters into credit agreement (NASDAQ:QCOM)
links.description: Qualcomm (NASDAQ:QCOM) has replaced and restated credit agreement providing for $4.47B in aggregate senior unsecured revolving loans, maturing on December 8, 2025.Proceeds from the credit agreement will be used for working capital, capital expenditures and other general corporate purposes.The credit agreement is unsecured and is not expected to be guaranteed by any subsidiary of the company.Shares -5% in premarket as Apple begins work on in-house cellular modem.
